data.description: This property has so much to offer!! Sitting on almost 13 acres, this 3 bed 2 bath home has been completely updated!! Large Kitchen that features stainless steel appliances and right off the kitchen is the huge family room with a wood burning fireplace that is perfect for those cold winters. With a split floor plan, two guest bedrooms on one side with a hall bath. Primary suite is a great size with an adjoining room with a hot tub!!! The huge screened in back porch is perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee in the morning overlooking the beautiful peaceful land that can be used for your very own livestock. There are several sheds and a barn that can be used as workshops, or storage.
